Friend -- There are just **three days** until our **final quarterly fundraising deadline** before Election Day.[
](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=2) We just need an additional **$6,000** to meet our quarterly goal to fully fund our upcoming TV, radio, and GOTV efforts. [
](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=3) Will you click **[here](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=4)** and help us meet this goal by making a donation of **[$50, $25, or even $10 now](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=5)**? Time is running very short for us to prepare for Election Day. It is critical for us to be able to deliver our positive conservative message throughout the largest district in the state, and having additional resources is key to this effort. [
](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=6) You have been a crucial part of this team, and with your continued help, we can ensure we have an opportunity to continue fighting to represent solid conservative Arkansas values in Washington. [
](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=7) Thank you for your support. [
](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=8) Congressman Bruce Westerman http://www.brucewesterman.com P.S. If just 100 **[supporters gave $60](https://www.brucewesterman.com/donate?e=87de312c4219248fa3631a1188a4b4f4&utm_source=westerman&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=donate_fec_3&n=9)** we would knock this out - will you be one of them today?
---
| Westerman For Congress · PO Box 21097, Hot Springs, AR 71903, United States
